high_descs: Turn right and go to the far side of the sink.
Pick up the left most spray bottle from the counter.
Turn around to the left.
Place the bottle in the black trash can.
Take a step to the left and face the toilet.
Take the spray bottle from the back of the toilet.
Step back to your right and face the trash can again.
Put the second spray bottle in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles into the trash can.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the wall, then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the leftmost spray bottle off of the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the small black bin in the corner of the room.
Put the spray bottle into the small black bin in the back left corner.
Walk up to the toilet to your left.
Pick up the spray bottle off of the toilet tank.
Walk back over to the small black bin in the corner of the room.
Put the spray bottle into the small black bin in front of the bottle that's already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles into a small black bin.

high_descs: turn right, move to the wall, then face the cabinet to the right
pick up the green spray bottle on top of the cabinet to the far left
turn around and face the black trash can
place the green spray bottle in the trash can
face the toilet tank slightly to the left of the trash can
pick up the green spray bottle on top of the toilet tank
return to facing the black trash can
place the spray bottle in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Dispose of two spray can bottles from around the bathroom
